    "created_at": "2014-03-17T21:22:37Z",
    "updated_at": "2014-03-17T21:22:37Z",
    "body": "This change was already discussed in January: https://mail.mozilla.org/pipermail/rust-dev/2014-January/007924.html\n\nThe purpose of this is to catch programmer errors where you have unexpected unbounded growth but picked the wrong way to deal with it. The next part of the plan is to add synchronous channels.\n",
